snippet.title: 【New Touhou Project Fan Game】The Touhou Empires【Under development】
snippet.description:
【Steam Store/Add on Wishlist!】
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1761210/The_Touhou_Empires/

"Touhou Project Fan Game x RTS!"

The Touhou Empires is a real-time strategy simulation game (RTS) in which you lead Touhou Project characters and fairies with various abilities to fight!

Players command Touhou Project's catactors and fairies to complete the prepared missions while responding to ever-changing situations!

Developer：Neetpia
Twitter：https://twitter.com/neetpia_ (@neetpia_)
　　　　https://twitter.com/__syousa__ (@__syousa__)
Publisher：Phoenixx
Site：https://phoenixx.ne.jp/
Twitter：https://twitter.com/Phoenixx_Inc (@Phoenixx_Inc)
YouTube：https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7GFEi5fF9-mfLIqnyzRMDw


#Phoenixx
